thread.title: Sonja Foster
thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by Sonja Foster

author: Sonja Foster
title: Sonja Foster
text: We have used Omega Car Rentals three times now and wouldn't hesitate to do so again on our next trip to New Zealand. The staff at the Wellington Airport Depot are fantastic and were great interacting with my 2 year old. The cars were clean and provided no hassles whatsoever. Very happy with their service.
